<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٦٧٧ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2587">سُلَيْمَانُ بْنُ حَرْبٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1619">حَمَّادُ بْنُ زَيْدٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/857">أَيُّوبَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4458">عِكْرِمَةَ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3732">ابْنِ عَبَّاسٍ </a><span class="special">﵄</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«بَعَثَنِي رَسُولُ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> مِنْ جَمْعٍ بِلَيْلٍ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>